snippet.title: She really needed our help, but it was too late..
snippet.description:
LuxuryDark: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-T_PzPlYvAg

*100,000 likes for next episode*

In this episode, Parker and Chester investigate a situation for a woman (Amber), whose uncle recently passed away and left her a house in his will. After attempting to go inside the house herself, Amber quickly left after she saw shadows and heard whispering inside. Parker and Chester go with Amber to the house to spend a couple nights there, while recording footage on cameras, attempting to find out what is living in the house.
